casebody.data:
In the Matter of ST. LAWRENCE COUNTY SUPPORT COLLECTION UNIT, etc., Respondent,
v.
Robert G. BOWMAN, Appellant. (And Another Related Proceeding.) Court of Appeals of New York. December 12, 2017

Appeal dismissed without costs, by the Court sua sponte, upon the ground that the order appealed from does not finally determine the proceedings within the meaning of the Constitution.
